{"id":547275,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/12/【立此存照】并不想起诉任全牛律师/","date":"2016-12-23T10:41:09Z","modified":"2016-12-23T09:54:05Z","title":"【立此存照】“并”不想起诉任全牛律师","content":"<p>【编者注】在被问及赵威近况时，其母回复道：“我不敢说”。赵威诉任全牛名誉纠纷案的撤诉申请中的撤诉理由是：<strong>本人并不想起诉任全牛律师</strong>。</p>\n<p>赵威同时还与“官派”律师董亚南、仉慧云解除了委托关系。</p>\n<blockquote style=\"width: 68%;\"><p><strong>相关阅读</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/12/%e8%80%83%e6%8b%89%e8%b5%b5%e5%a8%81%e8%af%89%e4%bb%bb%e5%85%a8%e7%89%9b%e5%be%8b%e5%b8%88%e5%90%8d%e8%aa%89%e6%9d%83%e7%ba%a0%e7%ba%b7%e4%b8%80%e6%a1%88%e5%b7%b2%e8%8e%b7%e5%87%86%e6%92%a4%e8%af%89/\">考拉赵威诉任全牛律师名誉权纠纷一案已获准撤诉</a></li>\n<li>中国数字时代<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%e8%80%83%e6%8b%89%e8%b5%b5%e5%a8%81/\" target=\"_blank\">考拉赵威</a>专题</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/xiucai1911/status/811876545040154624\" target=\"_blank\">@xiucai1911</a>：考拉（赵威）撤诉原因：本人并不想起诉任全牛律师，而且撤销官方指派的律师委托</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdXjqXgAA5APp.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-547276\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdXjqXgAA5APp.jpeg\" alt=\"c0rdxjqxgaa5app\" width=\"450\" height=\"799\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdXjqXgAA5APp.jpeg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdXjqXgAA5APp-169x300.jpeg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdXjqXgAA5APp-577x1024.jpeg 577w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdZcVWgAA-1kX.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-547278\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdZcVWgAA-1kX.jpeg\" alt=\"c0rdzcvwgaa-1kx\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdZcVWgAA-1kX.jpeg 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdZcVWgAA-1kX-225x300.jpeg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdZcVWgAA-1kX-768x1024.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdYk4XgAACdXZ.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-547277\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdYk4XgAACdXZ.jpeg\" alt=\"c0rdyk4xgaacdxz\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdYk4XgAACdXZ.jpeg 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdYk4XgAACdXZ-225x300.jpeg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/C0RdYk4XgAACdXZ-768x1024.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><em>另：作为李和平律师的助理，赵威曾经也为江西“乐平冤案”四处奔走过</em></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_547311\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/考拉乐平案.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-547311\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/考拉乐平案.jpg\" alt=\"%e8%80%83%e6%8b%89%e4%b9%90%e5%b9%b3%e6%a1%88\" width=\"525\" height=\"361\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/考拉乐平案.jpg 1328w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/考拉乐平案-300x206.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/考拉乐平案-768x529.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/考拉乐平案-1024x705.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">考拉微博截图</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[31355,19358,28140,29948,29947]}